edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.query

Class SubQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.query.Query
      • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.query.SubQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class SubQuery
extends Query
    A sub query may be part of a query or another sub query. If it is part of a query then it may reference a different resource then sibling sub queries. The sub queries can be combined using the Join clause in a query.
    Author:
    Jeremy R. Easton-Marks
